---
import Separator from "../../unitComponents/Separator.astro"
import Boxes from "../../../assets/images/Boxes.jpg";
---
<section class="w-full px-8 md:px-52 mt-32">
    <div class="w-full flex flex-col items-end">
        <h1 class="text-3xl md:text-5xl font-bold text-grisT">SPARE PARTS</h1>
        <div>
            <Separator/>
        </div>
    </div>
    <div class="w-full flex flex-col gap-10 font-bold">
        <p class="text-base md:text-lg text-grisT">
            Triaso spare parts are precisely engineered to deliver optimal performance, extending both component 
            lifespan and overall equipment durability. With unmatched quality and reliability, they help maintain peak 
            efficiency while minimizing downtime. <br>
            We understand the importance of keeping your equipment running non-stop. The operation of many other machines 
            depends on the reliability of your asphalt plant. <br>
            Strict quality control ensures the operation of your asphalt plant with low maintenance for many years.
        </p>
        <div class="w-full flex justify-center">
            <img src={Boxes.src} alt="" class="w-3/4 rounded-2xl">
        </div>
    </div>
</section>